We're Alex and Keri Spencer, the founders of Pact — and we wanted to personally welcome you.

We built Pact because we saw a problem that frustrated us: small businesses and independent professionals were being forced to choose between overpriced enterprise tools and clunky free alternatives just to get a document signed. That didn't sit right with us.

We believe that every freelancer, consultant, and small team deserves access to the same professional tools that big companies take for granted — without the big company price tag. That's why we built Pact to be simple, affordable, and genuinely useful from day one.

Here's what you can do right now:

Upload a PDF, place signature fields, and send it for signing — your recipient doesn't even need an account. You'll also find a built-in contact manager to keep your clients organized with notes, tags, and activity tracking.

Your 14-day trial gives you full access to everything. Take your time, explore the app, and send a few documents. If it's not for you, cancel anytime — no hard feelings, no hoops to jump through.

